All Implemented Interfaces:
Cursor
public class IteratorCursor
extends BaseCursor

Wraps a java.util.Iterator as a Cursor. All objects delivered by the Iterator must be of type com.esri.mo2.data.feat.Data otherwise the next() method will fail with a ClassCastException.
